Christopher Titus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Titus 0 Christopher Todd Titus (born October 1, 1964) is an American comedian and actor. He grew up in Newark, California. Titus came to network audiences with the eponymous FOX show Titus, of which he was the star, executive producer and co-creator. He is also a stand-up comedian whose act revolves around his dysfunctional family and shocking life experiences. Christopher_Todd_Titus ( born October_1_,_1964 ) is an_American_comedian_and_actor .
